/0-BC575AB8E2AB9833!2166"},"content":"       mongoDB docs 보고 mongoDB 서비스 설치하기        1. 데이터베이스 폴더 경로 만들기￼ mkdir C:\\Developer_Study\\TSPark\\MongoDB\\DB\\test￼2. mongod 데이터베이스 폴더 경로 바꾸기 시전￼ mongod --dbpath C:\\Developer_Study\\TSPark\\MongoDB\\DB\\test￼ /* mongod --auth --port 27017 --dbpath C:\\Developer_Study\\TSPark\\MongoDB\\DB\\test */￼3. Log파일 경로 만들기 & 파일 네이밍(무조건 ___.cfg)￼ C:\\Developer_Study\\TSPark\\MongoDB\\DB\\log_test￼ C:\\Developer_Study\\TSPark\\MongoDB\\DB\\log_test\\log_test.cfg￼4. 만들어진 Config파일 install￼ mongod --config \"C:\\Developer_Study\\TSPark\\MongoDB\\DB\\log_test\\testcfg.cfg\" --install￼5. config 파일 경로에 mongod.log가 생성되므로 로그 확인한다.￼6. 'net start mongodb' 로 cfg의 정보에 따른 mongod 를 시작한다.￼7. 'net stop mongodb'로 mongod를 끈다.￼8. 서비스 제거하고 싶다면.￼ \"C:\\Program Files\\MongoDB\\Server\\3.4\\bin\\mongod.exe\" --remove￼ or￼ mongod --remove￼    *. 1~7단계는 터미널 1개 창으로 시작과 작업과 끝을 다 할 수 있다.￼-> 보통은 터미널 1개로 mongod --dbpath C:\\Developer_Study\\TSPark\\MongoDB\\DB\\test 이런식으로 서비스를 시작하면￼터미널 1개를 새로 켜서 mongo 명령어로 작업을 해야했다.       ","html":"\n\t\t<div style=\"position:absolute;left:48px;top:139px;width:642px\">\n\t\t\t<h1 lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-size:16pt;color:#1e4e79;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\">mongoDB docs &#xBCF4;&#xACE0; mongoDB &#xC11C;&#xBE44;&#xC2A4; &#xC124;&#xCE58;&#xD558;&#xAE30;</h1>\n\t\t\t<br>\n\t\t\t<p lang=\"en-US\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:black;background-color:white\">1. &#xB370;&#xC774;&#xD130;&#xBCA0;&#xC774;&#xC2A4; &#xD3F4;&#xB354; &#xACBD;&#xB85C; &#xB9CC;&#xB4E4;&#xAE30;</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:black;background-color:white\">&#xFFFC;</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:black;background-color:white\">\tmkdir C:\\Developer_Study\\TSPark\\MongoDB\\DB\\test</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:black;background-color:white\">&#xFFFC;</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:black;background-color:white\">2. mongod &#xB370;&#xC774;&#xD130;&#xBCA0;&#xC774;&#xC2A4; &#xD3F4;&#xB354; &#xACBD;&#xB85C; &#xBC14;&#xAFB8;&#xAE30; &#xC2DC;&#xC804;</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:black;background-color:white\">&#xFFFC;</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:black;background-color:white\">\tmongod --dbpath C:\\Developer_Study\\TSPark\\MongoDB\\DB\\test</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:black;background-color:white\">&#xFFFC;</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:black;background-color:white\">\t/* mongod --auth --port 27017 --dbpath C:\\Developer_Study\\TSPark\\MongoDB\\DB\\test */</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:black;background-color:white\">&#xFFFC;</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:black;background-color:white\">3. Log&#xD30C;&#xC77C; &#xACBD;&#xB85C; &#xB9CC;&#xB4E4;&#xAE30; &amp; &#xD30C;&#xC77C; &#xB124;&#xC774;&#xBC0D;(&#xBB34;&#xC870;&#xAC74; ___.cfg)</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:black;background-color:white\">&#xFFFC;</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:black;background-color:white\">\tC:\\Developer_Study\\TSPark\\MongoDB\\DB\\log_test</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:black;background-color:white\">&#xFFFC;</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:black;background-color:white\">\tC:\\Developer_Study\\TSPark\\MongoDB\\DB\\log_test\\log_test.cfg</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:black;background-color:white\">&#xFFFC;</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:black;background-color:white\">4. &#xB9CC;&#xB4E4;&#xC5B4;&#xC9C4; Config&#xD30C;&#xC77C; install</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:black;background-color:white\">&#xFFFC;</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:black;background-color:white\">\tmongod --config &quot;C:\\Developer_Study\\TSPark\\MongoDB\\DB\\log_test\\testcfg.cfg&quot; --install</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:black;background-color:white\">&#xFFFC;</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:black;background-color:white\">5. config &#xD30C;&#xC77C; &#xACBD;&#xB85C;&#xC5D0; mongod.log&#xAC00; &#xC0DD;&#xC131;&#xB418;&#xBBC0;&#xB85C; &#xB85C;&#xADF8; &#xD655;&#xC778;&#xD55C;&#xB2E4;.</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:black;background-color:white\">&#xFFFC;</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:black;background-color:white\">6. &apos;net start mongodb&apos; &#xB85C; cfg&#xC758; &#xC815;&#xBCF4;&#xC5D0; &#xB530;&#xB978; mongod &#xB97C; &#xC2DC;&#xC791;&#xD55C;&#xB2E4;.</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:black;background-color:white\">&#xFFFC;</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:black;background-color:white\">7. &apos;net stop mongodb&apos;&#xB85C; mongod&#xB97C; &#xB048;&#xB2E4;.</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:black;background-color:white\">&#xFFFC;</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:black;background-color:white\">8. &#xC11C;&#xBE44;&#xC2A4; &#xC81C;&#xAC70;&#xD558;&#xACE0; &#xC2F6;&#xB2E4;&#xBA74;.</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:black;background-color:white\">&#xFFFC;</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:black;background-color:white\">\t&quot;C:\\Program Files\\MongoDB\\Server\\3.4\\bin\\mongod.exe&quot; --remove</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:black;background-color:white\">&#xFFFC;</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:black;background-color:white\">\tor</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:black;background-color:white\">&#xFFFC;</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:black;background-color:white\">\tmongod --remove</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:black;background-color:white\">&#xFFFC;</span></p>\n\t\t\t<p lang=\"en-US\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:black;background-color:white\">*. 1~7&#xB2E8;&#xACC4;&#xB294; &#xD130;&#xBBF8;&#xB110; 1&#xAC1C; &#xCC3D;&#xC73C;&#xB85C; &#xC2DC;&#xC791;&#xACFC; &#xC791;&#xC5C5;&#xACFC; &#xB05D;&#xC744; &#xB2E4; &#xD560; &#xC218; &#xC788;&#xB2E4;.</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:black;background-color:white\">&#xFFFC;</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:black;background-color:white\">-&gt; &#xBCF4;&#xD1B5;&#xC740; &#xD130;&#xBBF8;&#xB110; 1&#xAC1C;&#xB85C; mongod --dbpath C:\\Developer_Study\\TSPark\\MongoDB\\DB\\test &#xC774;&#xB7F0;&#xC2DD;&#xC73C;&#xB85C; &#xC11C;&#xBE44;&#xC2A4;&#xB97C; &#xC2DC;&#xC791;&#xD558;&#xBA74;</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:black;background-color:white\">&#xFFFC;</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:black;background-color:white\">&#xD130;&#xBBF8;&#xB110; 1&#xAC1C;&#xB97C; &#xC0C8;&#xB85C; &#xCF1C;&#xC11C; mongo &#xBA85;&#xB839;&#xC5B4;&#xB85C; &#xC791;&#xC5C5;&#xC744; &#xD574;&#xC57C;&#xD588;&#xB2E4;.</span></p>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\n\n"}}}